l-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"9cdff83d091b858a78acc86a2f1cb15d0380d0a8","tid":1668690,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d684fc2042c727c1b6cfce5f7d0b4cbfef84c866","tid":1668690,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Htga5eB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtga5eB.gif&h=0ac74e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f904a16dd780f9017975faedf535f4bd45c63c44","tid":1668690,"uid":198550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n好大對比<br />\n示威者連一隻路邊白鴿都會救<br />\n黑警會帶住佢一手養大既警犬上前線 唔比mask警犬戴都不特止 隻警犬震曬都仲要迫佢執勤"},{"pid":"ac6b353a9ef69c67c00070c6ca0f15220aacdf9b","tid":1668690,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"有冇專門對PoPo既文宣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"be330f711294cb1d1b4dd46824677cb925317156","tid":1668690,"uid":59450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"國際前線手足入嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/epJBQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/epJBQT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入黎"}]}